FBIS3-58536 "drweu011_h_94009" FBIS-WEU-94-011 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Jan 1994 GERMANY Several Injured in Arson Attack on Ludwigshafen Hostel LD1401121394 Berlin N-TV in German 1100 GMT 14 Jan 94 LD1401121394 Berlin N-TV Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Several residents were injured during an arson attack on an asylum-seekers' hostel in Ludwigshafen last night. One woman was taken to hospital suffering from smoke inhalation, another suffered serious bruising. A police spokesman said that the arsonists carried bulky refuse from the street into the hallway of the hostel and set fire to it. A 34-year-old man from Ludwigshafen has been arrested.
